{"__ud_title":"编写高质量 Skill：Claude 官方指南","__ud_tags":["Tools","Cloude code","aiskills"],"__ud_update_time":1772528526965,"__ud_create_time":1770960413757,"__ud_draft":false,"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":1,"id":"编写高质量-SkillClaude-官方指南"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"编写高质量 Skill：Claude 官方指南"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"一Skill-的本质三层渐进式架构"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"一、Skill 的本质：三层渐进式架构"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Skill 不只是一个 Markdown 文件，而是一套"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"渐进式披露（Progressive Disclosure）"},{"type":"text","text":" 机制："}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"层级内容加载时机作用"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"第一层"},{"type":"text","text":"YAML frontmatter始终加载到 system prompt让 AI 知道"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"何时"},{"type":"text","text":"使用这个 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"http://Skill第二层SKILL.md","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}],"text":"Skill"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"http://Skill第二层SKILL.md","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}},{"type":"bold"}],"text":"第二层"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"http://Skill第二层SKILL.md","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}],"text":"SKILL.md"},{"type":"text","text":" 正文任务相关时加载完整的指令和指导"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"第三层"},{"type":"text","text":"references/ 目录按需加载详细文档、API 参考等"}]},{"type":"blockquote","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这部分大家估计都很熟悉，快速跳过"}]}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"二文件结构规范"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"二、文件结构规范"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"bash"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"your-skill-name/\n├── SKILL.md              # 必需 - 主文件\n├── scripts/              # 可选 - 可执行脚本\n│   └── validate.py\n├── references/           # 可选 - 详细文档\n│   └── api-guide.md\n└── assets/               # 可选 - 模板等资源\n    └── template.md\n"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"硬性规则"},{"type":"text","text":"："}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"规则正确 ✅错误 ❌文件名"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"SKILL.mdskill.md"},{"type":"text","text":" / "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"SKILL.MD"},{"type":"text","text":"文件夹命名"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"my-cool-skillMy Cool Skill"},{"type":"text","text":" / "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"my_cool_skill"},{"type":"text","text":"是否包含 README不要在 Skill 内放 READMEREADME.md 会干扰解析"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"三YAML-Frontmatter决定-Skill-能否被触发"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"三、YAML Frontmatter：决定 Skill 能否被触发"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这是最关键的部分。"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"如果 frontmatter 写得不好，Skill 永远不会被调用，或者被过度调用。"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"最小格式"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"最小格式"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: your-skill-name\ndescription: What it does. Use when user asks to [specific phrases].\n---\n\n"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"Description-的核心公式"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Description 的核心公式"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"css"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"[它做什么] + [何时使用它] + [关键触发短语]\n"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"好-vs-差的对比"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"好 vs 差的对比"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"差的写法"},{"type":"text","text":"："}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# ❌ 太模糊，AI 不知道何时用\ndescription: Helps with projects.\n\n# ❌ 缺少触发条件\ndescription: Creates sophisticated multi-page documentation systems.\n\n# ❌ 太技术化，没有用户视角\ndescription: Implements the Project entity model with hierarchical relationships.\n"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"好的写法"},{"type":"text","text":"："}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# ✅ 具体 + 触发短语\ndescription: Analyzes Figma design files and generates developer handoff \ndocumentation. Use when user uploads .fig files, asks for \"design specs\", \n\"component documentation\", or \"design-to-code handoff\".\n\n# ✅ 动作明确 + 场景清晰\ndescription: Manages Linear project workflows including sprint planning, \ntask creation, and status tracking. Use when user mentions \"sprint\", \n\"Linear tasks\", \"project planning\", or asks to \"create tickets\".\n\n# ✅ 端到端流程 + 用户语言\ndescription: End-to-end customer onboarding workflow for PayFlow. \nHandles account creation, payment setup, and subscription management. \nUse when user says \"onboard new customer\", \"set up subscription\", \nor \"create PayFlow account\".\n"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"调试技巧"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"调试技巧"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"如果 Skill 不触发，直接问 AI："}]},{"type":"blockquote","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"When would you use the [skill-name] skill?\""}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"AI 会引用 description 字段来回答。根据它的回答调整你的 description。"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"四三类常见-Skill-模式"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"四、三类常见 Skill 模式"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"类型-1文档资产创建"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"类型 1：文档/资产创建"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"场景"},{"type":"text","text":"：生成一致、高质量的输出（文档、设计稿、代码等）"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"关键技术"},{"type":"text","text":"："}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"嵌入式风格指南"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"模板结构"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"输出前的质量检查清单"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"示例"},{"type":"text","text":"："},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"frontend-design"},{"type":"text","text":" skill"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"markdown"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Quality Checklist\nBefore finalizing output:\n- [ ] Typography hierarchy consistent\n- [ ] Color palette follows brand guide\n- [ ] Responsive breakpoints defined\n- [ ] Accessibility contrast ratios met\n"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"类型-2工作流程自动化"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"类型 2：工作流程自动化"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"场景"},{"type":"text","text":"：多步骤流程，需要一致的方法论"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"关键技术"},{"type":"text","text":"："}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"分步工作流 + 验证关卡"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"常见结构的模板"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"迭代细化循环"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"示例"},{"type":"text","text":"：顺序工作流编排"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"markdown"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Workflow: Onboard New Customer\n\n### Step 1: Create Account\nCall MCP tool: `create_customer`\nParameters: name, email, company\n\n### Step 2: Setup Payment\nCall MCP tool: `setup_payment_method`\nWait for: payment method verification\n⚠️ If fails: retry with alternate method\n\n### Step 3: Create Subscription\nCall MCP tool: `create_subscription`\nParameters: plan_id, customer_id (from Step 1)\n\n### Step 4: Send Welcome Email\nCall MCP tool: `send_email`\nTemplate: welcome_email_template\n"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"类型-3多-MCP-协调"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"类型 3：多 MCP 协调"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"场景"},{"type":"text","text":"：工作流程跨越多个服务"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"示例"},{"type":"text","text":"：设计到开发交接"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"markdown"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"### Phase 1: Design Export (Figma MCP)\n1. 从 Figma 导出设计资产\n2. 生成设计规格\n3. 创建资产清单\n\n### Phase 2: Asset Storage (Drive MCP)\n1. 在 Drive 中创建项目文件夹\n2. 上传所有资产\n3. 生成可共享链接\n\n### Phase 3: Task Creation (Linear MCP)\n1. 创建开发任务\n2. 将资产链接附加到任务\n3. 分配给工程团队\n\n### Phase 4: Notification (Slack MCP)\n1. 在 #engineering 发布交接摘要\n2. 包含资产链接和任务引用\n"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"五指令编写最佳实践"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"五、指令编写最佳实践"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"1-具体且可操作"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. 具体且可操作"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"markdown"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# ❌ 差\nMake sure to validate things properly\n\n# ✅ 好\nCRITICAL: Before calling create_project, verify:\n- Project name is non-empty\n- At least one team member assigned\n- Start date is not in the past\n\n"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"2-清晰引用资源"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"2. 清晰引用资源"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"markdown"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"在编写查询之前，请查阅 `references/api-patterns.md` 了解：\n- 速率限制指导\n- 分页模式\n- 错误代码和处理\n"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"3-包含错误处理"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"3. 包含错误处理"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"markdown"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Common Issues\n\n### MCP Connection Failed\n如果你看到\"Connection refused\"：\n1. 验证 MCP 服务器正在运行\n2. 确认 API 密钥有效\n3. 尝试重新连接\n"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"4-对抗懒惰"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"4. 对抗\"懒惰\""}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"markdown"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Performance Notes\n- Take your time to do this thoroughly\n- Quality is more important than speed\n- Do not skip validation steps\n"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"六常见问题排查"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"六、常见问题排查"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"问题-1Skill-不触发"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"问题 1：Skill 不触发"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"原因"},{"type":"text","text":"：description 太模糊或缺少触发短语"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"解决"},{"type":"text","text":"："}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"添加用户实际会说的关键词"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"提及相关文件类型（如 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":".fig"},{"type":"text","text":"、"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":".csv"},{"type":"text","text":"）"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"用 \"When would you use this skill?\" 调试"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"问题-2Skill-触发太频繁"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"问题 2：Skill 触发太频繁"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"解决"},{"type":"text","text":"：添加否定触发器"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"description: Advanced data analysis for CSV files. \nUse for statistical modeling, regression, clustering. \nDo NOT use for simple data exploration (use data-viz skill instead).\n"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"问题-3指令不被遵循"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"问题 3：指令不被遵循"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"常见原因"},{"type":"text","text":"："}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"指令太冗长 → 保持简洁，用列表"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"关键信息被埋没 → 用 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"## CRITICAL"},{"type":"text","text":" 标题"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"语言模糊 → 用代码/脚本替代自然语言"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"高级技巧"},{"type":"text","text":"：对于关键验证，用脚本而非语言指令"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","att